data.description: Step into comfort with this lovely brick and cedar 2-story home in the much desired Rolling Hills Subdivision, located in unincorporated Will County!   Once entered through double doors- off the idyllic attached wood porch, you are welcomed into a spacious living area with a cozy fireplace, perfect for large gatherings and relaxation.   The huge kitchen with an open floor plan is a chef's best friend, seamlessly connecting to the living room.   With 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, there's plenty of space for the whole family. The large unfinished basement offers endless possibilities for customization and expansion.   The 2.5 car dream garage provides ample parking and storage space. Enjoy the serene outdoors on the gorgeous deck overlooking a private yard that backs up against a beautiful tree line, creating a peaceful retreat right at home.   Newer windows, roof, and gutters all less than 5 years old. Double furnace/air units, and property owned water softener.  This property is a true gem, offering both comfort and functionality. Motivated Seller, offering a one year Home Warranty Service. Schedule your showing to see the unlimited potential this beauty has to offer....don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful home yours!
